ESP8266 Nest Remote Sensor

Use the ino file as firmware to for esp8266 with DS18B20

Replace SSID and wifi password in top of INO file to connect to your wifi.

Run server on the same network, replace IP and port with appropriate values.

Calibrate temperature sensor and set ranges to your pleasing.


Turns to off while below target temperature and turns the system on when remote temperature returns to target_temp - dwell

